  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "EVENT SALES CREW NEEDED 💼💥",
  "description": "<p>If you're outgoing, love meeting people, and want to get paid at fun events — this is your moment! We're on the lookout for energetic, responsible, and sales-driven individuals to join our <strong>Event Sales Crew</strong>.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>🛍️ <strong>What You’ll Be Doing:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Promote <strong>products at booths</strong></li>\n  <li>Actively <strong>approach and engage customers</strong> with a smile</li>\n  <li><strong>Support the team</strong> in driving sales, meeting targets &amp; keeping energy high</li>\n  <li>Represent brands in a fun and professional way</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>✅ <strong>We’re Looking For:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Confident, bubbly, and <strong>comfortable talking to anyone</strong></li>\n  <li>Able to work <strong>weekends/weekdays (event-based schedule)</strong></li>\n  <li>Physically fit to stand long hours and work on-site</li>\n  <li><strong>Sales/retail/event experience</strong> is a plus but not required</li>\n  <li>Reliable, punctual, and a great team player</li>\n  <li><strong>Singaporean/PR only.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🎁 <strong>What You’ll Get:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>WEEKLY payouts</strong> – no long wait!</li>\n  <li><strong>Bonuses</strong> for top sellers and strong performance 💰</li>\n  <li>Be part of exciting events &amp; campaigns </li>\n  <li>Work with a <strong>positive and supportive team</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>💌 <strong>Keen to Join Us?</strong></h3>\n<p>Drop us your <strong>resume or short intro!</strong><br>\nLet us know your <strong>availability</strong>, and we’ll link you up for the next event!</p>",
